<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>한국주류안전협회-정회원가입신청서</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/kalsa.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>

<div class="content-wrapper">
<section class="content-header">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="card card-primary card-outline">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5><b>정회원가입신청서</b></h5>
                        <hr>

                        <div class="form-row">
                        
                        <div class="form-group col-md-3"><label for="type">회원가입유형*</label></div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="form-check">
                                <label class="radio-inline">&nbsp;<input type="radio" id="type1" name="type" value="type1" checked>&nbsp;&nbsp;개인회원&nbsp;&nbsp;</label>
                                <label class="radio-inline">&nbsp;<input type="radio" id="type2" name="type" value="type2">&nbsp;&nbsp;단체회원&nbsp;&nbsp;</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="cname">회사명</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="cname" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="회사명">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="name">대표자명</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="name" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="대표자명">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="tel">전화번호</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="tel" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="전화번호">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="fax">팩스번호</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="fax" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="팩스번호">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="address">주소</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="address" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="주소">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="r_name">담당자명</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="r_name" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="담당자명">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="r_position">직위</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="r_position" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="직위">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="r_mobile">휴대폰번호</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="r_mobile" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="휴대폰번호">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="r_email">이메일</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="r_email" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="이메일">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="form-group col-md-3"></div>
                <div class="form-group col-md-9"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="card card-primary card-outline">
                    <div class="card-body">
    
                        <h5><b>협회 홈페이지 가입</b></h5>
                        <hr>
                        <div class="form-row">

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="id">사용자명(회원ID)</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="id" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="사용자명(회원ID)">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="email">회원가입용 e-mail</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="email" type="text" class="form-control" value="" placeholder="회원가입용 e-mail">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="user">홈페이지에 공개되는 이름</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="form-check">
                            <label class="radio-inline">&nbsp;<input type="radio" id="user1" name="user" value="user1" checked>&nbsp;&nbsp;사용자명&nbsp;&nbsp;</label>
                            <label class="radio-inline">&nbsp;<input type="radio" id="user2" name="user" value="user2">&nbsp;&nbsp;회사명&nbsp;&nbsp;</label>
                            <label class="radio-inline">&nbsp;<input type="radio" id="user3" name="user" value="user3">&nbsp;&nbsp;담당자명&nbsp;&nbsp;</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="comment">
                            참조1: 회사명 신청시, 홈페이지 담당자 이름이 회사명으로 가입됩니다.<br>
                            참조2: 사용자명(회원ID)는 영문과 숫자로만 구성됩니다.<br>
                            참조3: 비밀번호는 1234로 임의설정되며, 로그인 후 변경하시면 됩니다.<br>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                            <label for="signature">서명</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                            <div class="wrapper">
                                <canvas id="signature-pad" width="90%" height="200"></canvas>
                            </div>
                            <button type="button" id="clear" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">지우기</button>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                            <button type="button" id="save" class="btn btn-primary">저장하기</button>
                        </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</div>

